%% Diagram: Alt-Svc-driven HTTP/3 upgrade flow
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart LR
    A["TCP+TLS h2 connect"] --> B["Server returns Alt-Svc: h3=:443"]
    B --> C["Client caches alt-svc"]
    C --> D["Next request"]
    D --> E{"Cached entry valid?"}
    E -->|Yes| F["Open QUIC"]
    E -->|No| G["Stay on HTTP/2"]
    F --> H{"QUIC succeeds in race?"}
    H -->|Yes| I["Use HTTP/3, drop TCP"]
    H -->|No| J["Fall back, mark broken"]
